      <title>美元走强，中国将人民币中间价下调至一月份以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/china-weakens-yuan-fix-to-lowest-since-january-to-allow-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美元反弹促使政策制定者略微放松对人民币的控制，中国将人民币每日参考汇率下调至一月份以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/china-weakens-yuan-fix-to-lowest-since-january-to-allow-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
